<Base
  title="FAQ | Selling Your House to Jacob in Wichita KS"
  description="Common questions about selling your house for cash in Wichita KS. How fast can we close? Are there fees? What condition does the house need to be in?"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <p>Straight answers to the questions we hear most.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>How fast can you close?</h3><p>As fast as 7 days. We use a local Wichita title company. Once you accept the offer, you pick the closing date.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Do I need to clean or repair anything?</h3><p>No. We buy houses as-is. Leave whatever you don't want — we handle it.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>How do you determine your offer?</h3><p>We look at the property, recent sales in the neighborhood, condition, and what it will take to renovate. We build our number from real data, not guesswork.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Are there any fees?</h3><p>None. No commissions, no agent fees, no closing costs in most cases.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>What if I owe more than the house is worth?</h3><p>Call us anyway. We've worked through short sales and other complex situations before. We'll tell you honestly what options exist.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Is the process really that simple?</h3><p>Yes. Call, get an offer, pick a closing date, get paid. Most sellers are surprised at how straightforward it is.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>What areas do you buy in?</h3><p>All of Wichita and surrounding communities — Derby, Mulvane, Haysville, Andover, Augusta, El Dorado, Park City, Bel Aire, Valley Center, Goddard, Maize, and more.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>What types of properties do you buy?</h3><p>Single family homes, duplexes, multi-family, vacant lots, rental properties, inherited homes, and more.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="cta-block">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Still Have Questions?</h2>
      <p>Call Jacob directly. He answers his own phone.</p>
      <a href="tel:3168162983" class="btn-dark">Call (316) 816-2983</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
